Name:           nagstamon
Version:        3.2
Release:        alt1
Summary:        Nagios status monitor for the desktop
License:        GPLv2
Group:          Monitoring
Url:            http://nagstamon.ifw-dresden.de/
Source:         %name-%version.tar
%py3_requires   secretstorage sip
